&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://medium.freecodecamp.org/creating-a-web-performance-culture-inside-your-team-f00c0d79765f" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://medium.freecodecamp.org/creating-a-web-performance-culture-inside-your-team-f00c0d79765f&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
